          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've managed six-figure ad budgets across Meta, Google, and Instagram. I've also wasted more money than I'd like to admit on campaigns that went sideways overnight — a broken pixel here, an overspending ad set there, a CPA spike at 3 AM that nobody caught until morning.",
