        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That pattern changed when I started using ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bürch",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Formerly known as Revealbot, this platform sits quietly in the background and handles the tedious, time-sensitive parts of ad management so you can focus on strategy and creative work. If you've ever lost sleep wondering whether your campaigns are burning cash while you're away from your laptop, keep reading.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
