        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://bir.ch"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, Bürch is a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "marketing automation platform",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " built specifically for paid media teams. It connects directly to your Facebook Ads, Google Ads, and Instagram Ads accounts, then lets you set up automated rules, AI-powered budget optimization, and consolidated reporting — all from a single dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But here's what makes it different from the dozens of other tools claiming to do the same thing: Bürch was designed by people who actually run ads. The interface isn't bloated with features you'll never touch. Every function maps to a real pain point media buyers face daily.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think of it as a tireless assistant who monitors your campaigns 24/7, follows your exact instructions, and never takes a coffee break.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
