        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "These rules run every few minutes — not once a day like native platform schedulers. That speed matters. A campaign can overspend hundreds of dollars in the time it takes you to check your phone during dinner.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. AI-Driven Budget Optimization",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bürch doesn't just follow your rules blindly. Its AI layer analyzes performance trends across your campaigns and suggests (or automatically applies) budget redistributions that maximize your return.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instead of manually shifting money from underperforming ad sets to winners every morning, you define your optimization goals — ROAS, CPA, conversions — and the system handles the rest. It's like having a junior media buyer who never sleeps and never second-guesses the data.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Reporting That Doesn't Make You Want to Scream",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pulling data from three different ad platforms into a spreadsheet is nobody's idea of a good time. Bürch consolidates your Facebook, Google, and Instagram performance into unified dashboards. You can build custom reports, schedule automated delivery to stakeholders, and track cross-platform metrics side by side.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The reporting module alone justifies the subscription for agencies managing multiple clients. You save hours per week, and your clients get cleaner, more consistent updates.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Cross-Platform Control From One Place",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most marketers juggle at least two ad platforms. Bürch lets you manage rules, budgets, and reporting for Facebook, Google, and Instagram without switching tabs. This unified approach means your automation logic stays consistent, and you spot cross-channel patterns you'd otherwise miss.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For example, you might notice that your Google Search campaigns convert best when your Meta awareness campaigns are running at higher budgets. Bürch's cross-platform view makes those connections visible.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Speed and Reliability",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Rules execute in near real-time. Bürch checks your campaign data at intervals as short as a few minutes, which is significantly faster than Meta's built-in automated rules (which can take up to 30 minutes to trigger). In paid media, minutes matter. A rule that fires 25 minutes earlier can save you real money.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform also has a strong uptime track record. Ad automation is mission-critical infrastructure — you need it working when it matters most, during high-spend events like product launches or Black Friday.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. Transparent, Spend-Based Pricing",
