          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Bürch the same as Revealbot?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Revealbot rebranded to Bürch in 2024. The core product, team, and technology remain the same — it's the same ad automation platform with a new name and refreshed identity. Existing users experienced no disruption during the transition.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What ad platforms does Bürch support?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bürch currently supports Facebook Ads (Meta), Instagram Ads, and Google Ads. You can connect multiple ad accounts from each platform and manage them all from a single dashboard with unified rules and reporting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does Bürch cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Essential plan starts at $49/month (or $45/month billed annually with a 20% discount) for accounts with up to $10K in monthly ad spend. Pricing scales with your total ad spend across all connected accounts. There are no overage charges on the Essential tier.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Bürch really save me money on ads?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Bürch's automated rules prevent overspend by pausing underperforming ads in near real-time, and its AI budget optimization shifts spend toward your best-performing campaigns. Most users report saving 5–10 hours per week on manual monitoring and seeing improved ROAS within the first month.",
            "marks": []
          }
